snippet.title: Hob | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover your role as the sole protagonist on a strange and beautiful world torn apart by competing life forms. Others have tried and failed. Now, it's your chance: make it home.

For the prequel comic, see hobgame.com/comic
Official site: hobgame.com
Official facebook: facebook.com/hobthegame
Official twitter: twitter.com/runicgames

Hob releases Tuesday, September 26, on PS4, GOG, and Steam!
